    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant attention from its next owner. While it does start and run, the engine exhibits a noticeable knock and the transmission shifts roughly, suggesting a need for mechanical overhaul. The exterior has several large dents, significant paint fading, and some areas of surface rust, while the interior shows heavy wear with torn upholstery and some non-functional electronics. This would be an ideal project car for someone with mechanical expertise or a source for parts, but it is not currently recommended for daily use without major repairs.",
