    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to offer this superlative vehicle, currently maintained in pristine, showroom condition. Every facet of this automobile, from its flawless exterior finish to its immaculate, wear-free interior, reflects a history of meticulous stewardship. Mechanically, the vehicle operates with the precision and refinement of a new unit, having undergone a rigorous inspection to ensure it meets our exacting standards. This represents a rare acquisition opportunity for the discerning buyer who requires uncompromising quality and aesthetic perfection.",
      "price": 44900.0,
