    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly collector-grade example that defies its age. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, resulting in an exterior finish that retains its deep, showroom luster without a single swirl mark, stone chip, or blemish. Inside, the cabin remains in time-capsule condition; the premium leather seats show no signs of bolster wear, and the factory-original scent persists. Every electronic component, from the precision navigation system to the ambient lighting, functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a comprehensive service history with every scheduled maintenance performed exclusively by certified technicians. Underneath, the chassis is remarkably clean, showing no signs of inclement weather exposure. This sale includes all original keys, the owner\u2019s manual portfolio, and a documented history file. For the discerning buyer seeking a vehicle that looks, feels, and drives like new, this is an unparalleled opportunity.",
      "price": 44800.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
