      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously gotta see this beauty \u2013 it\u2019s basically like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve absolutely babied this car, and it's in pristine condition inside and out. No scratches, no dents, and the interior is still smelling fresh. It\u2019s been my pride and joy, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy this perfect ride. Drop me a message if you want to come take a look!",
      "price": 43500.0,
