      "description": "Offering a collector-grade E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, complete with six individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This example is equipped with the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a variable M differential lock. Crucial preventative maintenance has been executed, including a comprehensive subframe reinforcement and a full VANOS system overhaul with upgraded seals. The suspension geometry is factory-perfect, riding on refreshed bushings for precise turn-in. The exterior retains its factory depth with flawless panel gaps, while the Nappa leather interior remains supple with zero bolster wear. A mechanically transparent, turn-key masterpiece for the discerning purist.",
